Motivation

The motivation behind this analyis is to see if teams / individuals using a certain strategy have certain demographics.

for (name in demo_names) {
  dependent<- name

}

dependent<- "Temporal.Demand"

for (name in TLX_Scale_Names) {
  
  dependent<- name
  
  y_label_ind <- "Count"

         Dominate.Strategy,

    ggplot(data = plot_data_ind) +
    geom_histogram(aes(x = .data[[dependent]])) +

  )
